ckquote><br />\n咁租私家車算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好好奇點解之前有人話租到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dc4161ac82b3641acec81bccbd3646b88cb8f2","tid":432014,"uid":104092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:35:37.000Z","msg":"做咩坐250cc? 用單車環島啦"},{"pid":"3452106f48edfc09680891464db3f0b7c550be02","tid":432014,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:02:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未試過，但諗緊11月去</blockquote><br />\n巴打plan哂行程未？</blockquote><br />\n仲未諗好哂，諗緊兜一半就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大概高雄開始逆時針去，行下台東花蓮，然後花蓮上武嶺落返花蓮，跟住去台北還車飲下酒落下club咁。<br />\n<br />\n聽d朋友講花蓮上武嶺好辛苦，台中上武嶺會易d,  但我對台中同西邊果邊d景點又無咩興趣，仲諗緊點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a04899fcb21b7a03eb1347127a67d36a65bf54","tid":432014,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>250一樣上到山<br />\n租重機你等住俾租車鋪屈錢</blockquote><br />\n有係台灣租過150街車玩過<br />\n但今次係同台灣frd去<br />\n佢地有250cc以上個牌<br />\n所以想一齊租大車周圍去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外地人租唔到300 所以你可以唔使諗</blockquote><br />\n咁租私家車算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好好奇點解之前有人話租到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢可能有考到本地重機牌 一係偷雞"},{"pid":"196c33190b6e83a8af30d35f7c3fe656f465d426","tid":432014,"uid":34677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>未試過，但諗緊11月去</blockquote><br />\n巴打plan哂行程未？</blockquote><br />\n仲未諗好哂，諗緊兜一半就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大概高雄開始逆時針去，行下台東花蓮，然後花蓮上武嶺落返花蓮，跟住去台北還車飲下酒落下club咁。<br />\n<br />\n聽d朋友講花蓮上武嶺好辛苦，台中上武嶺會易d,  但我對台中同西邊果邊d景點又無咩興趣，仲諗緊點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太魯閣上有可能會車量控制"},{"pid":"a71fdf791246c95401d896b9cc10dc4db0b249c2","tid":432014,"uid":14810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T12:19:53.000Z","msg":"上武嶺緊係台中上南投再上清境再上武嶺，條路好走好多，由花蓮方向上梨山再上武嶺條路又多落石又封路唔多建議行呢條<br />\n<br />\n上武嶺記得帶相機或露營，星星多到影唔曬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/201843_10add56ebe7aae0f136b09847ca02eb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F201843_10add56ebe7aae0f136b09847ca02eb8.jpg&h=46b73c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早係武嶺停車場朋友幫我影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/201846_996d8c43de106da4b4b3fa205fe61acf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F201846_996d8c43de106da4b4b3fa205fe61acf.jpg&h=f4c47921&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05420d41604194be6bea000e1c49386d56d9f417","tid":432014,"uid":38047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:28:46.000Z","msg":"上武嶺的話係咪租細cc好啲？<br />\n話哂都灣多路窄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47fc8cb453aed94f4d444e1ad074fc20d97813cc","tid":432014,"uid":142151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T16:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上武嶺緊係台中上南投再上清境再上武嶺，條路好走好多，由花蓮方向上梨山再上武嶺條路又多落石又封路唔多建議行呢條<br />\n<br />\n上武嶺記得帶相機或露營，星星多到影唔曬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/201843_10add56ebe7aae0f136b09847ca02eb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F201843_10add56ebe7aae0f136b09847ca02eb8.jpg&h=46b73c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早係武嶺停車場朋友幫我影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/201846_996d8c43de106da4b4b3fa205fe61acf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F201846_996d8c43de106da4b4b3fa205fe61acf.jpg&h=f4c47921&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n雲豹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有部<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n巴打住台灣？ <br />\n<br />\nbtw影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ef9abb89342a1a301479cd95d5c73da771c98f","tid":432014,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:01:17.000Z","msg":"影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b5cede2f607d26fdcbc0797193f29c383db3a0","tid":432014,"uid":35063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:05:23.000Z","msg":"單車都係兩個6<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f486f844ed8577aa48fa91e8987a2f2229151a","tid":432014,"uid":41695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上武嶺緊係台中上南投再上清境再上武嶺，條路好走好多，由花蓮方向上梨山再上武嶺條路又多落石又封路唔多建議行呢條<br />\n<br />\n上武嶺記得帶相機或露營，星星多到影唔曬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/201843_10add56ebe7aae0f136b09847ca02eb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F201843_10add56ebe7aae0f136b09847ca02eb8.jpg&h=46b73c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早係武嶺停車場朋友幫我影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/12/201846_996d8c43de106da4b4b3fa205fe61acf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F12%2F201846_996d8c43de106da4b4b3fa205fe61acf.jpg&h=f4c47921&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n影得好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁影要點set 用咩鏡 求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546c05f9987a4e6ff54f22ba1acf7991febc1a0c","tid":432014,"uid":142151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T17:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做咩坐250cc? 用單車環島啦</blockquote><br />\n班frd懶撚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會自己試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打試過？"},{"pid":"3f07c7d74636df3916bc0efccaf24b590740e1ac","tid":432014,"uid":14810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"鏡就問朋友借左支16-35 f2.8黎玩，色水真係好正又sharp，不過就算用一般鏡影都ok啦，風景相都係靚境出靚相架啦<br />\n<br />\n影星空Setting就ISO6400 光圈就F8到F16，快門最低30秒起跳，有B快門就用B，到時按實際需要去調，記得帶腳架同快門線，相機我就用6D,apsc機驚iso太高既話就調落3200或1800，但曝光時間要加長<br />\n<br />\n車其實125cc羊仔都夠上，當然愈大力愈好啦，我就建議羊仔租smax，棍仔租T2就夠用啦，如果有租車店肯搏大霧租大車比你就自己揀岩心水，冇就上面兩架夠玩啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw分享多兩張比大家，台中高美濕地唔錯可以影日落<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/025053_73190b8ba74915c15bc4d83c695fa4f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F025053_73190b8ba74915c15bc4d83c695fa4f7.jpg&h=1d12eef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台南又係必去，好野食多到食唔完，相就台南黃金海岸影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/025056_29bea0c605e01014656a5efc0bb584b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F025056_29bea0c605e01014656a5efc0bb584b2.jpg&h=a34337fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路線既話想知再答"},{"pid":"ba78a17b1f3ce22ae0a4607eb8dcb2dd4861a52e","tid":432014,"uid":61830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"求路線同月左幾多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}